      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for a dedicated project or as a source for spare parts. The engine starts but suffers from a persistent leak and overheating issues, while the suspension feels very worn and requires a complete overhaul. Externally, there are several large dents and the clear coat is peeling significantly across the hood and roof. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics, so please expect to invest time and effort into restoration.",
