      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This specimen represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that remains in a state of absolute preservation. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. This is an uncompromising opportunity to acquire a vehicle of investment-grade quality.",
