    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you won't believe how gorgeous this beauty is\u2014it\u2019s seriously like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping it in pristine, flawless condition, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and looks brand new, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
